The paper focuses on video captioning, which involves computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also incorporates semantic attributes and attention mechanism, which are related to natural language processing and machine learning. Hence, cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also likely categories.
